campaignName.description:
The current campaign name obtained is the campaign name of dy.
The JSON format should include:
{
  "status": "slug",
  "variation": "page_slug"
}
"variation" is the label for GA4 tracking, and the value for "status" is the page slug participating in the experiment. For example, if the pageList value is: slug-a,slug-b, then the dy configuration should include two variations:
{
  "status": "slug-a",
  "variation": "page_slug-a"
},
{
  "status": "slug-b",
  "variation": "page_slug-b"
}
